Symbol.Script_3D:
! Fan Powered Box
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT A/2, B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ADD -A/2, -B/2, 0 BLOCK A, B, ZZYZX ADD dBox, B, dBox BLOCK boxX, boxY, boxZ DEL 1 DEL 1
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
ConPosY_1= MIN (MAX (-B/2+ConWallThickness_1+ConWidth_1/2, ConPosY_1), B/2-ConWallThickness_1-ConWidth_1/2) ConPosY_2= MIN (MAX (-B/2+ConWallThickness_2+ConWidth_2/2, ConPosY_2), B/2-ConWallThickness_2-ConWidth_2/2)
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 13, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 13 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Fan Powered Box
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A/2, -B/2, 1, A/2, -B/2, 1, A/2, B/2, 1, -A/2, B/2, 1 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A/2+dBox, B/2, 1, -A/2+dBox+boxX, B/2, 1, -A/2+dBox+boxX, B/2+boxY, 1, -A/2+dBox, B/2+boxY, 1 ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 13, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 13 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Fan Powered Box
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
boxX= 0.300 boxY= 0.100 boxZ= 0.100 dBox= 0.050
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z
Symbol.Script_UI:
! Fan Powered Box
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_vis_attr[4][4] FOR i = 1 TO 4 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 2 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 7
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14
DIM ui_con_type[2] ui_con_type[1] = 0 ui_con_type[2] = 0
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS ALL ui_vis_attr = ui_vis_attr, ui_centerline_vars = 0, ui_con_type = ui_con_type, ui_system_var_pos = 2, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Fan Powered Box
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 1 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "A" RANGE [2*dBox+boxX, ] A = MAX (A, 2*dBox+boxX) VALUES "B" RANGE [0.10, ] B = MAX (B, 0.10) VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [2*dBox+boxZ, ] ZZYZX = MAX (2*dBox+boxZ, ZZYZX) ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 2
! --- 1st CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Впускное Соединение Воздуховода`
ConDVecX = -1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = -1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0, ] IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21] - 2) > EPS THEN IF ConDepth_1>ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2 THEN ConDepth_1= ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2 PARAMETERS ConDepth_1= ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2 ENDIF IF ConWidth_1>B-ConWallThickness_1*2 THEN ConWidth_1= B-ConWallThickness_1*2 PARAMETERS ConWidth_1=B-ConWallThickness_1*2 ENDIF VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE [0.001, B-ConWallThickness_1*2] ConWidth_1= MIN (MAX (0.001, ConWidth_1), B-ConWallThickness_1*2) VALUES "ConDepth_1" RANGE [0.001, ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2] ConDepth_1= MIN (MAX (0.001, ConDepth_1), ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2) ELSE IF ConWidth_1>MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2, B-ConWallThickness_1*2) THEN ConWidth_1= MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2, B-ConWallThickness_1*2) PARAMETERS ConWidth_1= MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2, B-ConWallThickness_1*2) ENDIF VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE [0.001, MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2, B-ConWallThickness_1*2)] ConWidth_1= MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_1*2, B-ConWallThickness_1*2, ConWidth_1) PARAMETERS ConDepth_1=ConWidth_1 ConDepth_1=ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1" ENDIF
PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = -A/2 VALUES "ConPosY_1" RANGE [-B/2+ConWallThickness_1+ConWidth_1/2, B/2-ConWallThickness_1-ConWidth_1/2] PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = ZZYZX/2 ConPosY_1= MIN (MAX (-B/2+ConWallThickness_1+ConWidth_1/2, ConPosY_1), B/2-ConWallThickness_1-ConWidth_1/2) ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
! --- 2nd CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 2 ConName = `Выпускное Соединение Воздуховода`
ConDVecX = 1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = 1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConLength_2" RANGE [0, ] IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[2][21] - 2) > EPS THEN IF ConDepth_2>ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2 THEN ConDepth_2= ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2 PARAMETERS ConDepth_2= ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2 ENDIF IF ConWidth_2>B-ConWallThickness_2*2 THEN ConWidth_2= B-ConWallThickness_2*2 PARAMETERS ConWidth_2=B-ConWallThickness_2*2 ENDIF VALUES "ConWidth_2" RANGE [0.001, B-ConWallThickness_2*2] ConWidth_2= MIN (MAX (0.001, ConWidth_2), B-ConWallThickness_2*2) VALUES "ConDepth_2" RANGE [0.001, ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2] ConDepth_2= MIN (MAX (0.001, ConDepth_2), ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2) ELSE IF ConWidth_2>MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2, B-ConWallThickness_2*2) THEN ConWidth_2= MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2, B-ConWallThickness_2*2) PARAMETERS ConWidth_2= MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2, B-ConWallThickness_2*2) ENDIF VALUES "ConWidth_2" RANGE [0.001, MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2, B-ConWallThickness_2*2)] ConWidth_2= MIN (ZZYZX-ConWallThickness_2*2, B-ConWallThickness_2*2, ConWidth_2) PARAMETERS ConDepth_2=ConWidth_2 ConDepth_2=ConWidth_2 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_2" ENDIF
PARAMETERS ConPosX_2 = A/2 VALUES "ConPosY_2" RANGE [-B/2+ConWallThickness_2+ConWidth_2/2, B/2-ConWallThickness_2-ConWidth_2/2] PARAMETERS ConPosZ_2 = ZZYZX/2 ConPosY_2= MIN (MAX (-B/2+ConWallThickness_2+ConWidth_2/2, ConPosY_2), B/2-ConWallThickness_2-ConWidth_2/2) ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_2, ConPosY = ConPosY_2, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_2, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_2, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_2, ConWidth = ConWidth_2, ConDepth = ConDepth_2, ConLength = ConLength_2, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_2, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_2, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_2, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_2, ConToolType = ConToolType_2, ConStatus = ConStatus_2, ConType_2 = ConType_2, ConConnectorType_2 = ConConnectorType_2, ConSystem_2 = ConSystem_2, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_2, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
